<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <!-- <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0 user-scalable=0" /> -->
    <meta content="width=1715,height=764" name="viewport" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../common_finish/common/css/common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.9.0/css/all.min.css" />
    <title>차시마무리 평가</title>
    <script src="../../common_finish/common/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_finish/common/js/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_finish/common/js/jquery.ui.touch-punch.min.js"></script>
    <script id="MathJax-script" async src="../../common_finish/common/js/MathJax/tex-chtml.js"></script>
    <script type="module" src="../../common_finish/common/js/main.js"></script>
  </head>
  <style>
    #q1 .qe_area .ans {
      width: 250px;
    }
  </style>
  <body>
    <div id="scaleWrapper">
      <div id="intro" class="intro_2">
        <div class="inner">
          <div class="top">
            <span lang="y" class="danwon_num">2단원</span>
            <span lang="y" class="danwon_name">평면도형</span>
          </div>
          <h1 lang="y" class="title">마무리 평가</h1>
          <p lang="y" class="qe_num">문항수 : 5개</p>
          <p lang="y" class="guide">
            답안 제출 기회는 2번씩 있어요.<br />
            준비가 되면 시작 버튼을 눌러 주세요.<br />
            준비되었나요?
          </p>
          <button lang="y" type="button" class="intro_btn">시작하기</button>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="quest">
        <div class="nav">
          <div class="pagination">
            <button type="button" class="p1 on" aria-current="page" aria-label="현재 페이지1">
              <span>1</span>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="p2" aria-label="페이지2">
              <span>2</span>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="p3" aria-label="페이지3">
              <span>3</span>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="p4" aria-label="페이지4">
              <span>4</span>
            </button>
            <button type="button" class="p5" aria-label="페이지5">
              <span>5</span>
            </button>
          </div>
          <div class="center">
            <button type="button" class="submit disable"><img src="../../common_finish/common/img/mamuri/ic_check.svg" alt="" aria-hidden="true" />제출</button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="q1" class="page on">
          <div class="bg">
            <div class="mid_tit">
              <span lang="y" class="q-num">문제</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">비커에 소금 12 g을 녹여 소금물 200 g을 만들었습니다. 이 소금물에서 소금물 양에 대한 소금의 비율을 구한 것을 고르세요.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="qe_area">
              <fieldset class="item_wrap vertical5" role="group" aria-labelledby="q1-label">
                <legend id="q1-label" class="sr-only"></legend>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q1" value="item1" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">0.03</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q1" value="item2" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">0.04</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q1" value="item3" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">0.05</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q1" value="item4" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">0.06</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q1" value="item5" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">0.07</span>
                </label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="q2" class="page">
          <div class="bg">
            <div class="mid_tit">
              <span lang="y" class="q-num">문제</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">규원이네 마을의 넓이는 12 ㎢이고 인구는 45600명입니다. 마을의 넓이에 대한 인구의 비율은 얼마인가요?</span>
            </div>
            <div class="qe_area">
              <fieldset class="item_wrap vertical5" role="group" aria-labelledby="q2-label">
                <legend id="q2-label" class="sr-only"></legend>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q2" value="item1" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">3500</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q2" value="item2" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">3600</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q2" value="item3" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">3700</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q2" value="item4" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">3800</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q2" value="item5" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">3900</span>
                </label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="q3" class="page">
          <div class="bg">
            <div class="mid_tit">
              <span lang="y" class="q-num">문제</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">표를 보고 오토바이와 자동차 중 어느 것이 더 빨리 달렸는지 구해 보세요.</span>
            </div>
            <div class="qe_area center">
              <div class="qe">
                <img src="../../common_finish/common/img/mamuri/qe/EMA614_05_SU_0100(3).png" alt="" />
              </div>
              <fieldset class="item_wrap" role="group" aria-labelledby="q3-label">
                <legend id="q3-label" class="sr-only"></legend>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q3" value="item1" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">오토바이</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q3" value="item2" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">자동차</span>
                </label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="q4" class="page">
          <div class="bg">
            <div class="mid_tit">
              <span lang="y" class="q-num">문제</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">초록 버스는 180 km를 가는 데 2시간이 걸렸고, 노랑 버스는 279 km를 가는 데 3시간이 걸렸습니다. 두 버스의 걸린 시간에 대한 간 거리의 비율을 비교하여 어느 버스가 더 빠른지 골라 보세요. </span>
            </div>
            <div class="qe_area center">
              <fieldset class="item_wrap" role="group" aria-labelledby="q4-label">
                <legend id="q4-label" class="sr-only">다음 중 알맞은 수를 모두 선택하세요</legend>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q4" value="item1" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">초록 버스</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q4" value="item2" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">노랑 버스</span>
                </label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div id="q5" class="page">
          <div class="bg">
            <div class="mid_tit">
              <span lang="y" class="q-num">문제</span>
              <span lang="y" class="txt">민지와 슬기가 야구 연습을 했습니다. 두 친구 중 타율이 더 높은 친구의 이름을 써 보세요. </span>
            </div>
            <div class="qe_area center">
              <div class="t-box">
                • 민지: 나는 25타수 중에서 안타를 7개 쳤어.<br />
                • 슬기: 나는 20타수 중에서 안타를 5개 쳤어.
              </div>
              <fieldset class="item_wrap vertical" role="group" aria-labelledby="q5-label">
                <legend id="q5-label" class="sr-only">다음 중 알맞은 수를 모두 선택하세요</legend>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q5" value="item1" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">민지</span>
                </label>
                <label class="item">
                  <input type="checkbox" name="q5" value="item2" class="sr-only" />
                  <span lang="y" class="txt">슬기</span>
                </label>
              </fieldset>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="submitModal" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
          <p lang="y" class="modal-message">이대로 제출하겠습니까?</p>
          <div class="modal-buttons">
            <button lang="y" type="button" class="modal-cancel">취소</button>
            <button lang="y" type="button" class="modal-confirm">제출</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script>
      /* 
    각 문항의 유형 + (답안 예시)
    1. : 입력형           input.answer
    2. : item 선택형      .answer.selected
    3. : 선택지 선택형     .answer:checked
    4. : D&D              .dropped-item
    5. : 선긋기           
    */
      window.questionTypes = [3, 3, 2, 2, 2];
      window.correctAnswers = {
        1: ["item4"],
        2: ["item4"],
        3: ["item1"],
        4: ["item2"],
        5: ["item1"],
      };
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
